                            <comment id="13178749" author="marcin84" created="Tue, 3 Jan 2012 14:24:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tried to solve on my own, and the problem occurs because of invalid XML configuration. The BAM example that is in binary distribution &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;bean id=&quot;activities&quot; class=&quot;org.apache.camel.example.bam.MyActivities&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;jpaTemplate&quot; ref=&quot;jpaTemplate&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&quot;transactionTemplate&quot; ref=&quot;transactionTemplate&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be changed to &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;bean id=&quot;activities&quot; class=&quot;org.apache.camel.example.bam.MyActivities&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;constructor-arg&amp;gt;&amp;lt;ref bean=&quot;jpaTemplate&quot;/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;constructor-arg&amp;gt;&amp;lt;ref bean=&quot;transactionTemplate&quot;/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/constructor-arg&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Second version calls valid constructor for ProcessBuilder which creates ProcessName. The first one leaves process name as null.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13178820" author="davsclaus" created="Tue, 3 Jan 2012 17:03:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I fixed the ProcessBuilder in camel-bam to create the processor name if not explicit configured.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
